The paper discusses open problems related to gathering and patrolling by mobile robots, which are topics commonly studied in the field of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the use of models and algorithms, which could fall under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence in solving these problems (cs.AI), as well as the use of control systems (cs.SY) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
